headline: Synopsys Q4 Earnings Surpass Estimates, Revenues Rise Y/Y
summary: SNPS posts a Q4 beat as revenues surge on strong Time-Based, Upfront Product and EDA growth, while offering upbeat FY26 and Q1 outlooks.
